==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Proximal pronouns in Catalan (''[[ací]]''), French (''[[ce]]'', ''[[ici]]'', ''[[ci]]''), Italian (''[[ci]]''), Romanian (''[[ici]]'')

===Particle===
# (particle denoting [[proximity]]) -[[here]]
#: The particle can appear before or after a demonstrative correlative. For example, ''tio '''ĉi''''' (or '''''ĉi''' [[tio]]'') means "this [thing]", ''tiu '''ĉi''''' means "this one", and ''tie '''ĉi''''' means "[that location] [[here]]".

====Antonyms====
* ''[[for]]'': [[distant]] (adverbial particle of distance)

